\begin_layout Subsubsection
with example lapack/blas
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Here is a table for performance of Armadillo with 64-bits lapack and blas
 on my desktop (Core i7-6700 @ 3.40 GHz), with TDM-GCC 64-bits compiler.
 The CPU time is measured by std::clock(), which is only accurate at the
 level of 10ms.
 Since the IO work is not intense, these times could approximate the elapsed
 time/wall clock time.
\end_layout

